OL,12, North doubles West'sF1NTGand East bids 
OL,13,F2DGto show diamonds and a higher suit. 
OL,14, With three diamonds West might pass,   
OL,15, but here he bidsF2H,Gwhich East passes.
OL,16, In this case there is no eight-card fit
OL,17, but it can be difficult for opponents  
OL,18, to double with confidence, particularly
OL,19, if they have not discussed a defence.  
