OL,7,GThe annualCSt John's Wood Auction Pairs
OL,8, produced a record amount of #10,850,   
OL,9, all of which was distributed to the top
OL,10, pairs. The purchaser of the winning    
OL,11, pair received #6,510. Top four were:   
OL,12, 1 Norman and Richard Selway            
OL,13, 2 Ian Panto and Nikolas Sandqvist      
OL,14, 3 Geoffrey Broskal and Akram Zaman     
OL,15, 4 Su Burn and Phil King                
OL,17, Early enquiries for the St John's Wood 
OL,18, first Teams Auction recommended. Phone 
OL,19,G0171 286 7465.                         
