OL,7,GIn the final of the 1996-97CGold Cup   
OL,8, Alan Mould, Gary Byett, John Collings, 
OL,9, Martin Jones, Paul Bowyer and John     
OL,10, Helme beat Ian Reissman, Mike Perkins, 
OL,11, Raymond and Sally Brock, Steve Eginton 
OL,12, and Su Burn.                           
